WITH PostStats AS (
    SELECT 
        p.Id AS PostId,
        p.PostTypeId,
        COUNT(c.Id) AS CommentCount,
        COUNT(v.Id) AS VoteCount,
        MAX(p.CreationDate) AS LastActivityDate,
        SUM(CASE WHEN v.VoteTypeId = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS UpVotes,
        SUM(CASE WHEN v.VoteTypeId = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DownVotes
    FROM 
        Posts p
    LEFT JOIN 
        Comments c ON p.Id = c.PostId
    LEFT JOIN 
        Votes v ON p.Id = v.PostId
    GROUP BY 
        p.Id, p.PostTypeId
),
UserStats AS (
    SELECT 
        u.Id AS UserId,
        COUNT(b.Id) AS BadgeCount,
        SUM(u.Reputation) AS TotalReputation,
        COUNT(DISTINCT p.Id) AS PostCount
    FROM 
        Users u
    LEFT JOIN 
        Badges b ON u.Id = b.UserId
    LEFT JOIN 
        Posts p ON u.Id = p.OwnerUserId
    GROUP BY 
        u.Id
)
SELECT 
    ps.PostId,
    ps.PostTypeId,
    ps.CommentCount,
    ps.VoteCount,
    ps.LastActivityDate,
    ps.UpVotes,
    ps.DownVotes,
    us.UserId,
    us.BadgeCount,
    us.TotalReputation,
    us.PostCount
FROM 
    PostStats ps
JOIN 
    UserStats us ON ps.PostTypeId = us.UserId
ORDER BY 
    ps.VoteCount DESC, 
    ps.CommentCount DESC
LIMIT 100

GROUP BY "Posts0"."Id", "Posts0"."PostTypeId") AS "t2"
INNER JOIN (SELECT MIN("Users"."Id") AS "USERID", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM("Users"."Reputation") AS "TOTALREPUTATION", COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."Id") AS "POSTCOUNT"
FROM "Users"
LEFT JOIN "Badges" ON "Users"."Id" = "Badges"."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "Users"."Id" = "s1"."OwnerUserId"
GROUP BY "Users"."Id") AS "t5" ON "t2"."POSTTYPEID0" = "t5"."USERID"
ORDER BY "t2"."VOTECOUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t2"."COMMENTCOUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 100
